^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Well done John. Let's discuss the bidding first. I play that you still can super accept with 4 card support over a transfer, even with a 2N opener even if partner has zero points, the 9 card fit makes it possible you can make 4H. And partner almost never has zero points. So, I would have bid 4H with John's hand, although 3 hearts is certainly quite reasonable, and what most people would have done. |
